name: MayhemMix
description:
A chaotic, nonsensical mix between a lot of models (protogen, anything, deliberate, dreamlike, Elysium, HD, my own mix models, WD, and more that I have forgotten).

Due to how many models were shoved in, it has a wide range of ability.

vae is already baked in.

Is somewhat capable of generating nsfw.
